    <title type="html"><![CDATA[ruby正则表达式]]></title>
    <link href="http://piggytommy.github.com/blog/rubyzheng-ze-biao-da-shi.html/"/>
    <updated>2012-08-30T13:24:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://piggytommy.github.com/blog/rubyzheng-ze-biao-da-shi</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>ruby正则表达式的使用一直是用的少，忘的快。把必要把常用的用法记录一下， 增强记忆力。</p>

<h3 id="ruby">ruby正则表达式的建立</h3>
<ul>
  <li>使用”//”建立</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="sr">/ruby/</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<ul>
  <li>使用类方法建立</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="no">Regexp</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">new</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">str</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<ul>
  <li>使用”%r” 建立</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="sr">%r(ruby)</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="sr">%r&lt;ruby&gt;</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="sr">%r|ruby|</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<h3 id="section">正则表达式的匹配</h3>
<ul>
  <li>使用”=~” 进行匹配</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="sr">/ruby/</span> <span class="o">=~</span> <span class="s2">&quot;i love ruby&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>匹配成功时返回匹配成功的起始位置， 不成功时返回nil</p>

<ul>
  <li>以一般文字进行匹配</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="sr">/ruby/</span> <span class="o">=~</span> <span class="s2">&quot;ruby is cool.&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>以上代码只是单纯的匹配字符串里面是否包含相同的文字</p>

<ul>
  <li>匹配行尾和行首</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="sr">/^java$/</span> <span class="o">=~</span> <span class="s2">&quot;java&quot;</span>                     <span class="c1">#匹配成功</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="sr">/^java$/</span> <span class="o">=~</span> <span class="s2">&quot;java is easy to learn. &quot;</span>  <span class="c1">#匹配失败</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>”^”和”$”是具有特殊意义的字符， 即转义字符(meta-character)</p>

<ul>
  <li>指定需要匹配成功的文字范围</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="o">[</span><span class="no">AB</span><span class="o">]</span>             <span class="o">-----</span><span class="n">A</span> <span class="err">或者</span> <span class="n">B</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="o">[</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">z</span><span class="o">]</span>            <span class="o">-----</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="err">到</span><span class="n">z</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="o">[</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">zA</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">z_</span><span class="o">]</span>        <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">所有英文字母与</span><span class="n">_</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">可用来匹配变量名</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="o">[^</span><span class="no">AB</span><span class="o">]</span>            <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">匹配</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="n">B</span><span class="err">以外的内容</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="o">[^</span><span class="n">A</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="no">Za</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">z</span><span class="o">]</span>        <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">匹配英文字母以外内容</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<ul>
  <li>匹配任意字符</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="sr">/ru.y/</span><span class="o">=~</span><span class="s2">&quot;ruby&quot;</span>                 <span class="c1">#匹配成功</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<ul>
  <li>使用反斜杠的表达式</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="p">\</span><span class="n">s</span>       <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">匹配空白（会与空白字符，</span> <span class="err">定位字符，换行字符，</span> <span class="err">换页字符匹配成功）</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="p">\</span><span class="n">d</span>       <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">与</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="o">~</span><span class="mi">9</span><span class="err">之间的数字匹配成功</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="p">\</span><span class="n">w</span>       <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">与英文和数字匹配成功</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="p">\</span><span class="n">A</span>       <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">与字符串前端匹配成功</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">注意与行首和行尾的区别</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="p">\</span><span class="n">Z</span>       <span class="o">-----</span><span class="err">与字符串末端进行匹配</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<ul>
  <li>反复出现</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="ruby"><span class="line"><span class="o">*</span>        <span class="o">------</span><span class="err">出现</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="err">次以上</span>
