</span><span class="line"><span class="p">?</span>        <span class="o">------</span><span class="err">出现</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="err">次或者</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="err">次</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">?</span>       <span class="o">------</span><span class="err">出现</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="err">次以上，但取最短的匹配结果</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="o">+</span><span class="p">?</span>       <span class="o">------</span><span class="err">出现</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="err">次以上，但取最短的匹配结果</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<ul>
  <li>正则表达式的选项</li>
</ul>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
